<h4>Hi <%= @user %>!</h4>

<p>Your cabpool has been updated by admin. The following are the updated details of it :-</p>
<p>Capacity of the cabpool : <%= @updated_cabpool.number_of_people %></p>
<p>Arrival Time To Office : <%= @updated_cabpool.timein %></p>
<p>Departure Time From Office : <%= @updated_cabpool.timeout %></p>
<p>Remarks : <%= @updated_cabpool.remarks %></p>
<p>Route :- </p>
<ul>
  <li>Start point : <%= @updated_cabpool.ordered_localities.first.name %></li>
  <li>Via :-</li>
  <ol>
    <% @updated_cabpool.ordered_localities.drop(1).each do |locality| %>
        <li><%= locality.name %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ol>
</ul>
<p>Members of cabpool :- </p>
<ul>
<% @updated_cabpool.users.each do |user| %>
    <li><strong><%= user.name %></strong></li>
<% end %>
</ul>

<p>Know more on <%= link_to 'Danglay', your_cabpools_url, target: '_blank'%></p>
<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>Danglay</p>